name: __ENiagaraModuleDependencyUsage
doc: Defines different usages for a niagara script's module dependecies.

None: Default entry to catch invalid usages
Spawn: Evaluate when the script is called during the spawn phase.
Update: Evaluate when the script is called during the update phase.
Event: Evaluate when the script is called in an event context.
SimulationStage: Evaluate when the script is called in a simulation stage.
